personal data we collect
,
our purposes for using it
,
how we sell or share it
and
how to opt out
, and
how long we keep it
.
We refer to all our mobile game products, together with our other services and websites, including slotslimited.com, as "Services" in this Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy also explains your choices about how we use personal data about you. Using our Services indicates your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree with this Privacy Policy, do not access, or use our Services or interact with any other aspect of our business.
